WEBVTT

00:00:00.636 --> 00:00:02.354
GERSHON Shuster.

00:00:02.354 --> 00:00:04.190
KAUNAS, LITVA.

00:00:08.027 --> 00:00:10.012
azoy az

00:00:10.339 --> 00:00:12.577
mentshn hobn gedarft hobn

00:00:14.743 --> 00:00:15.969
me zol,

00:00:16.059 --> 00:00:19.766
es zol heysn az zey geyen arbetn oyfn erodrom,

00:00:20.127 --> 00:00:22.855
az zey zoln krign in di arbets-karte

00:00:23.097 --> 00:00:25.504
a shtempl az zey zaynen geven.

00:00:27.012 --> 00:00:30.128
ober zey hobn aleyn nit gevelt geyn.

00:00:30.792 --> 00:00:33.469
iz geven in geto aza fakh

00:00:34.521 --> 00:00:35.893
far kinder

00:00:35.893 --> 00:00:37.057
vi tsu zayn

00:00:37.057 --> 00:00:39.577
a malekh, flegt men dos onrufn.

00:00:39.921 --> 00:00:41.585
heyst dos az

00:00:42.250 --> 00:00:43.999
a yunger yingl

00:00:45.068 --> 00:00:48.133
fun draytsn fertsn yor, fuftsn yor,

00:00:48.730 --> 00:00:52.858
fleg geyn far a groysn mentshn oyfn erodrom arbetn

00:00:53.573 --> 00:00:55.997
un derfar flegt er krign opesn.

00:00:57.049 --> 00:00:59.793
ikh bin oykh geven aza malekh.

00:01:01.453 --> 00:01:03.525
ikh bin gegangen far mentshn

00:01:03.525 --> 00:01:05.446
arbetn oyfn erodrom.

00:01:05.942 --> 00:01:07.201
far derfar

00:01:07.815 --> 00:01:10.408
fleg ikh krign a lebl broyt

00:01:10.887 --> 00:01:12.315
un a teler zup,

00:01:13.941 --> 00:01:15.470
az ikh fleg kumen

00:01:15.713 --> 00:01:16.924
fun ovnt

00:01:16.924 --> 00:01:18.237
fun aerodrom.

00:01:20.286 --> 00:01:21.697
dem teler zup

00:01:21.822 --> 00:01:23.604
fleg ikh oyfesn

00:01:24.167 --> 00:01:25.612
bay dem mentshn

00:01:26.091 --> 00:01:27.269
bay velkhn,

00:01:27.269 --> 00:01:29.021
bay velkhn ikh bin gegangen,

00:01:29.533 --> 00:01:32.665
un dem lebl broyt fleg ikh brengen in shtub

00:01:33.077 --> 00:01:34.353
far alemen.

00:01:36.992 --> 00:01:38.319
mayn tate

00:01:38.595 --> 00:01:40.175
vos er hot gearbet

00:01:41.110 --> 00:01:42.504
bay di daytshn

00:01:43.742 --> 00:01:45.990
flegt, flegt oykh brengen

00:01:46.380 --> 00:01:47.797
tsu bislekh

00:01:47.797 --> 00:01:48.950
esnvarg,

00:01:49.986 --> 00:01:52.376
un dos hot undz zeyer geholfn

00:01:53.800 --> 00:01:56.274
vayl in geto

00:01:56.382 --> 00:01:57.675
mitn esn,

00:01:57.782 --> 00:01:59.193
mit esnvarg,

00:01:59.655 --> 00:02:02.349
iz geven zeyer a groyser problem,

00:02:05.781 --> 00:02:07.631
vayle mentshn

00:02:07.907 --> 00:02:09.858
hobn nit gehat vos tsum esn.

00:02:10.978 --> 00:02:13.166
un men flegt shtarbn fun hunger,

00:02:14.978 --> 00:02:16.845
iber hoypt azelkhe

00:02:17.830 --> 00:02:19.478
eltere mentshn

00:02:20.580 --> 00:02:23.105
vos hobn shoyn nit gekent geyn arbetn

00:02:23.888 --> 00:02:26.222
un zey hobn nit gekent

00:02:26.720 --> 00:02:31.324
vi mir flegn zogn oyskombinirn avu nit iz

00:02:31.920 --> 00:02:32.842
esn.

00:02:34.114 --> 00:02:35.610
nokh flegt men

00:02:37.253 --> 00:02:39.221
krign esn durkh azoy

00:02:39.227 --> 00:02:42.815
vos oyf der arbets-ort, vu me flegt geyn arbetn,

00:02:43.311 --> 00:02:44.958
flegt men baytn

00:02:45.808 --> 00:02:46.932
zakhn

00:02:48.373 --> 00:02:50.847
mit di litviner oyf esnvarg.

00:02:53.149 --> 00:02:56.906
nu, dos heyst azoy vi, lomir zogn, me t- flegt nemen

00:02:57.199 --> 00:02:58.458
a zeyger

00:02:59.494 --> 00:03:03.200
ave- avek- avekgeyn bay der arbet. bay der arbet flegt zikh trefn

00:03:03.595 --> 00:03:07.014
litviner mit yidn flegn zikh trefn, flegt zayn

00:03:07.425 --> 00:03:09.815
bay di zelbe arbet. farshteyt zikh

00:03:09.815 --> 00:03:12.135
di litviner hobn geton besere arbet.

00:03:12.285 --> 00:03:14.658
di yidn hobn geton di shmutsike arbet.

00:03:15.947 --> 00:03:18.523
ober di litviner velndik hobn

00:03:18.715 --> 00:03:19.924
far bilik

00:03:20.352 --> 00:03:21.983
farsheydene zakhn

00:03:22.309 --> 00:03:24.564
flegn zey brengen a shtikl broyt,

00:03:24.570 --> 00:03:26.167
a shtikl vursht.

00:03:27.726 --> 00:03:29.930
iz geven azoy, far a zeyger

00:03:30.004 --> 00:03:32.293
flegt men krign a halbn lebn broyt,

00:03:33.784 --> 00:03:35.448
a shtikele vursht.

00:03:36.180 --> 00:03:39.920
far a kostyum flegt UNK avektrogn a kostyum

00:03:40.146 --> 00:03:42.755
flegt men krign dortn a kilo fleysh.

00:03:43.723 --> 00:03:48.678
azoy hot men gebitn, azoy az yeder eyner hot zikh gedreyt vi er hot nor gekent,

00:03:49.393 --> 00:03:51.867
nor tsum krign a shtikl broyt.

00:03:54.793 --> 00:03:56.727
nu, derfar,

00:03:56.903 --> 00:04:00.609
vi ikh hob shoyn gezogt, bin ikh gegangen als a malekh oyfn erodrom

00:04:00.666 --> 00:04:01.875
far mentshn

00:04:02.303 --> 00:04:05.503
un ikh hob oykhet geholfn in familye

00:04:07.315 --> 00:04:08.929
mit a shtikl broyt.

00:04:12.782 --> 00:04:14.092
nu, vayter,

00:04:16.461 --> 00:04:17.231
dem

00:04:18.503 --> 00:04:22.783
dem zeks un tsvantsikstn tsu finf un tsvantsikstn

00:04:26.012 --> 00:04:27.288
oktober

00:04:30.113 --> 00:04:31.896
iz aroys a bafel

00:04:34.146 --> 00:04:34.978
az dem

00:04:34.978 --> 00:04:37.194
akht un tsvantsikstn oktober

00:04:39.006 --> 00:04:40.502
darfn ale

00:04:41.014 --> 00:04:42.442
geto-mentshn

00:04:44.592 --> 00:04:46.543
zikh tsuzamenklaybn

00:04:46.701 --> 00:04:47.960
in geto

00:04:48.777 --> 00:04:50.121
oyf a plats.

