00:05:56.766 --> 00:05:58.802
hobn zikh fun gants geto

00:06:00.259 --> 00:06:06.294
ongehoybn tsuzamenklaybn di yidn oyf dem plats.

00:06:07.077 --> 00:06:08.539
yung un alt,

00:06:08.916 --> 00:06:10.479
kleyn un groys,

00:06:11.565 --> 00:06:13.567
ale hobn zikh geklibn.

