men hot arumgeringlt dem gantsn plats,

00:06:32.676 --> 00:06:34.205
avekgeshtelt

00:06:34.583 --> 00:06:36.230
koyln-varfers.

00:06:38.295 --> 00:06:39.841
es iz gekumen

